ComicInfo.Summary:
While Ryu fights for survival against the full power of martial arts master Oro, Gill and the Secret Society reveal their plans for the world - plans that include a new Street Fighter Tournament! Plus, Dan & Sakura have an encounter with the King of the Jungle - Blanka!
*List of covers and their creators:* Cover | Name | Creator(s) | Sidebar Location | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- A | Regular Story Cover | Genzoman | 1 | B | Ultra Jam Puzzle Cover B (5 of 12) | Jeffrey Cruz | 2 | C | 1:10 Retailer Incentive Homage Cover C | FooRay | 3 | D | 1:20 Retailer Incentive Street Fighter V Cover D | Kandoken | 4 | Notes:
Cover B is part six of a twelve part connecting cover image made up of all the Ultra Jam Puzzle covers for issues #1-12. The 1:10 Retailer Incentive Homage Cover C is a homage of the cover of Wizard: The Comics Magazine #34.
